      "id": 1867727727902049,
      "definition": {
        "title": "Pod Health & Stability Indicators",
        "show_title": true,
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 5591098956764444,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "**Degradation Indicators**\n\nWatch for these signals:\n- **CPU throttling > 0** - Pods hitting CPU limits\n- **Memory near limits** - Risk of OOM kills\n- **Rising in-flight requests** - Possible saturation\n- **Increasing latency** - DB or service degradation\n- **Thread/FD exhaustion** - Resource leak indicators",
              "background_color": "yellow",
              "font_size": "14",
              "text_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
